《'''All Out'''》（风格化下[[全部大写|全部大写]]）是{{tsl|en|virtual|虚拟乐队|虚拟}}[[女子音乐组合|女子音乐组合]][[K/DA|K/DA]]首张迷你专辑。专辑于2020年11月6日由[[Riot_Games|Riot Games]]和[[Stone_Music_Entertainment|Stone Music Entertainment]]发行<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.forbes.com/sites/mikestubbs/2020/10/02/all-out-is-the-first-ep-from-league-of-legends-pop-group-kda-and-its-out-next-month/#2d3cc03c3968|title=ALL OUT Is The First EP From ‘League Of Legends’ Pop Group K/DA And It’s Out Next Month|author=Mike Stubbs|work=Forbes|date=2020-10-02|accessdate=2020-11-09|archive-date=2020-10-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201010140708/https://www.forbes.com/sites/mikestubbs/2020/10/02/all-out-is-the-first-ep-from-league-of-legends-pop-group-kda-and-its-out-next-month/#2d3cc03c3968|dead-url=no}}</ref>，收录了五首歌曲，演唱者除最初的阵容[[(G)I-DLE|(G)I-DLE]]、[[麥狄森·碧兒|麥狄森·碧兒]]和[[杰拉·伯恩斯|杰拉·伯恩斯]]，还包括[[碧·米勒|碧·米勒]]、Wolftyla、[[刘柏辛|刘柏辛]]、萨勒芬妮、[[金·彼特拉斯|金·彼特拉斯]]、Aluna、{{tsl|en|Bekuh Boom|Bekuh Boom}}、[[TWICE|TWICE]]和安妮卡·韦尔斯（Annika Wells）等具有影响力的艺人。每首歌均由K/DA组合的一位虚构成员负责制作。

先导单曲〈[[The_Baddest_(K/DA歌曲)|The Baddest]]〉于2020年8月27日发行，在《[[告示牌_(雜誌)|告示牌]]》{{tsl|en|World Digital Song Sales|世界数字音乐销量榜}}位列第1，而主打单曲〈[[More_(K/DA歌曲)|More]]〉则于2020年10月28日发行<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://hypebae.com/2020/10/kda-all-out-debut-ep-collaborators-full-list-twice-gidle-madison-beer-wolftyle-kim-petras-league-of-legends-k-pop-riot-games|title=MADISON BEER, TWICE, (G)I-DLE AND MORE COLLABORATE ON K/DA'S DEBUT EP 'ALL OUT'|author=Kim Ye Eun|work=Hypebae|date=2020-10-16|accessdate=2020-11-09|archive-date=2020-11-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201102134541/https://hypebae.com/2020/10/kda-all-out-debut-ep-collaborators-full-list-twice-gidle-madison-beer-wolftyle-kim-petras-league-of-legends-k-pop-riot-games|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

==背景及推广== 
〈[[The_Baddest_(K/DA歌曲)|The Baddest]]〉于2020年8月27日发行后，K/DA陆续在社交媒体帐号发表阿狸、阿卡丽、伊芙琳、卡莎的宣传照，并附带标签“#Wherewevebeen #KDA #CallingBlades”<ref>{{cite news|url=https://twitter.com/KDA_MUSIC/status/1301203237177978880|title=Come back stronger. #WHEREWEVEBEEN #AKALI #KDA #CALLINGALLBLADES|website=Twitter|author=@KDA_MUSIC|date=2020-09-03|accessdate=2020-11-09|archive-date=2020-09-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200902170100/https://twitter.com/KDA_MUSIC/status/1301203237177978880|dead-url=no}}</ref>。9月5日，K/DA确认会与[[虚拟YouTuber|虚拟YouTuber]]萨勒芬妮进行合作。自萨勒芬妮一直在[[Twitter|Twitter]]、[[Instagram|Instagram]]和[[SoundCloud|SoundCloud]]发帖，显示个人形象的画风与游戏其他角色一致以来，玩家便猜测双方会有合作<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.polygon.com/2020/9/4/21422960/league-of-legends-pop-group-kda-seraphine-riot-worlds-blades-collaboration-song|title=League of Legends’ fictional pop group K/DA is working on a song with fictional influencer Seraphine|website=Polygon|author=Austen Goslin|date=2020-09-04|accessdate=2020-11-09|archive-date=2020-11-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201105111625/https://www.polygon.com/2020/9/4/21422960/league-of-legends-pop-group-kda-seraphine-riot-worlds-blades-collaboration-song|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |last1=Rand |first1=Emily |title=Riot Games announces K/DA's comeback |url=https://tv5.espn.com/esports/story/_/id/29747458/riot-games-announces-k-da-comeback |website=ESPN.com |accessdate=2020-11-09 |date=2020-08-27 |archive-date=2020-08-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200827213709/https://tv5.espn.com/esports/story/_/id/29747458/riot-games-announces-k-da-comeback |dead-url=no }}</ref>。萨勒芬妮在个人Instagram帐号确认会担任专辑其中一位制作人<ref>{{cite instagram |user=seradotwav |postid=CEuIsfxjhaK |date=2020-09-04 |title=i know a lot of you have been guessing, but i can finally say that i'm collaborating with @kda_music!! i'll be working with them to help produce their album and even feature on an upcoming track 🎵 this is seriously a dream come true and it's all possible thanks to you 😭💜💞thank you so much for your support!! |access-date=2020-10-15}}</ref>。与此同时，Riot发行K/DA组合网络连载漫画《K/DA：和音》第一章，讲述了组合录歌的幕后故事、成员间的交流、经历及冒险<ref>{{cite news|url=https://dotesports.com/league-of-legends/news/k-da-drops-new-comic-series-featuring-seraphine|title=K/DA drops new comic series featuring Seraphine|website=Dot Esports|author=Rachel Samples|date=2020-09-05|accessdate=2020-11-09|archive-date=2020-09-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200910124546/https://dotesports.com/league-of-legends/news/k-da-drops-new-comic-series-featuring-seraphine|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=https://dontfeedthegamers.com/league-of-legends-kda-comic-seraphine/|title=League of Legends Releases New K/DA Comic Featuring Seraphine|website=Don’t Feed the Gamers|author=Ryan "Cinna" Carrier|date=2020-09-06|accessdate=2020-11-09|archive-date=2020-11-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201109140809/https://dontfeedthegamers.com/league-of-legends-kda-comic-seraphine/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=https://comicbook.com/gaming/news/league-of-legends-kda-harmonies-comics/|title=League of Legends Reveals K/DA Comic Series|website=comicbook.com|author=Rollin Bishop|date=2020-09-06|accessdate=2020-11-09|archive-date=2020-09-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200923002948/https://comicbook.com/gaming/news/league-of-legends-kda-harmonies-comics/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。9月28日，K/DA发布官方应援荧光棒，其外貌为舞台麦克风，把手采用黑色螺旋设计。同时公布了粉丝名称Blades<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://sg.news.yahoo.com/baddest-official-k-da-lightstick-122712051.html|title=Be the baddest with this official K/DA lightstick|author=Christian V|work=SG Yahoo NEws|date=2020-09-28|accessdate=2020-11-09|archive-date=2020-10-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201021102554/https://sg.news.yahoo.com/baddest-official-k-da-lightstick-122712051.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

