10月2日，专辑名称《All Out》、正式封面及多张宣传照连同发行时间一起公布<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.invenglobal.com/articles/12370/league-of-legends-kda-announces-debut-ep-revealing-new-official-look|title=League of Legends' K/DA announces debut EP, revealing new official look|website=Invenglobal|author=Lara Lunardi|date=2020-10-02|accessdate=2020-11-09|archive-date=2020-11-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201109140809/https://www.invenglobal.com/articles/12370/league-of-legends-kda-announces-debut-ep-revealing-new-official-look|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=https://dotesports.com/league-of-legends/news/k-das-newest-ep-titled-all-out-given-official-release-date|title=K/DA’s newest EP titled ALL OUT given official release date|website=Dot Esports|author=Samuel O'Dwyer|date=2020-10-02|accessdate=2020-11-09|archive-date=2020-10-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201002213034/https://dotesports.com/league-of-legends/news/k-das-newest-ep-titled-all-out-given-official-release-date|dead-url=no}}</ref>。消息指主打歌将在[[英雄联盟2020赛季全球总决赛|英雄联盟2020赛季全球总决赛]]上表演，谣传会是英雄联盟下一位英雄的萨勒芬妮将会登台表演<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://win.gg/news/5713/k-da-to-release-ep-all-out-new-song-debuts-at-worlds-2020-finals|title=K/DA to release EP ALL OUT, new song debuts at Worlds 2020|author=Christian V|work=WIN.gg|date=2020-10-03|accessdate=2020-11-09|archive-date=2020-11-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201109140809/https://win.gg/news/5713/k-da-to-release-ep-all-out-new-song-debuts-at-worlds-2020-finals|dead-url=no}}</ref>。歌单于10月9日公布<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.bandwagon.asia/articles/riot-games-league-of-legends-k-pop-k-da-ahri-akali-evelynn-kaisa-true-damage-seraphine-collaboration-all-out-debut-ep-2020|title=Everything to know about Riot Games' virtual K-Pop group K/DA and their upcoming debut EP, ALL OUT|author=Kara Bodegon|work=Bandwagon|date=2020-10-19|accessdate=2020-11-09|archive-date=2020-11-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201101102402/https://www.bandwagon.asia/articles/riot-games-league-of-legends-k-pop-k-da-ahri-akali-evelynn-kaisa-true-damage-seraphine-collaboration-all-out-debut-ep-2020|dead-url=no}}</ref>。10月12日，Riot Games上线K/DA成员阿狸、阿卡丽、伊芙琳、卡莎以及萨勒芬妮的新皮肤<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://dotesports.com/league-of-legends/news/riot-reveals-new-k-da-skin-line-called-all-out-featuring-seraphine|title=Riot reveals new K/DA skin line called ALL OUT featuring Seraphine|author=Tyler Esguerra|work=Dot Esports|date=2020-10-11|accessdate=2020-11-09|archive-date=2020-11-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201101092223/https://dotesports.com/league-of-legends/news/riot-reveals-new-k-da-skin-line-called-all-out-featuring-seraphine|dead-url=no}}</ref>。萨勒芬妮的皮肤会随着她不断成长为流行巨星而变化，从“萨勒芬妮新秀”（Seraphine Indie）、“萨勒芬妮明日之星”（Seraphine Rising Star）、“萨勒芬妮超级巨星”（'Seraphine Superstar）。虽然萨勒芬妮是英雄的消息尚未得到澄清，但Riot Games次日宣布萨勒芬妮是有音乐主题技能的新冠军法师<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.nme.com/en_au/news/gaming-news/riot-games-announces-new-league-of-legends-champion-seraphine-2782421|title=Riot Games announces new ‘League Of Legends’ champion, Seraphine|author=Surej Singh|work=NME|date=2020-10-13|accessdate=2020-11-09|archive-date=2020-10-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201018122115/https://www.nme.com/en_au/news/gaming-news/riot-games-announces-new-league-of-legends-champion-seraphine-2782421|dead-url=no}}</ref>。10月16日，Riot Games公布五首歌曲的表演者，人数达10人<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.invenglobal.com/articles/12501/kda-all-out-ep-to-feature-g-idle-kim-petras-madison-beer-lexie-liu-twice-and-more|title=K/DA ALL OUT EP to feature (G)-IDLE, Kim Petras, Madison Beer, Lexie Liu, TWICE, and more|website=Invenglobal|author=Lara Lunardi|date=2020-10-16|accessdate=2020-11-09|archive-date=2020-11-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201109140810/https://www.invenglobal.com/articles/12501/kda-all-out-ep-to-feature-g-idle-kim-petras-madison-beer-lexie-liu-twice-and-more|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

〈[[More_(K/DA歌曲)|More]]〉发行两天后，Riot在《[[英雄联盟|英雄联盟]]》、《[[符文之地传奇|符文之地传奇]]》、《[[云顶之弈|云顶之弈]]》和《[[英雄联盟：激斗峡谷|英雄联盟：激斗峡谷]]》等游戏举行各色活动及比赛，为《All Out》的发行预热。{{校對翻譯句|其中《符文之地传奇》推出“K/DA All Out活动通行证”（K/DA All Out Event Pass）。持有该通行证的玩家可获得K/DA的限量史诗指令卡，购买奖励更多的白金赛事通行证，参加新游戏模式“K/DA星之力量”（K/DA Star Power）。玩家可以直接挑选K/DA成员作为游戏主角色。另外还有收录特别表演曲目的“K/DA board”。《云顶之弈》中，Feather Knight、Fluffy Tail、Whining、Horn和Flash以K/DA主题的新形象示人。11月12日，玩家可以通过“K/DA Little Legend Knows”或组合的表演购买通行证。在《激斗峡谷》，玩家用K/DA英雄参与游戏、执行任务，或是购买All Out皮肤可获得更多奖励|time=2020-11-09T14:20:26+00:00}}<ref>{{cite web|url=http://gametoc.hankyung.com/news/articleView.html?idxno=56418|script-title=ko:라이엇 게임즈, K/DA 컴백 기념 대규모 이벤트 진행|trans-title=Riot Games holds a large-scale event to celebrate K/DA comeback|author=Seo Dong-min|work=Gametoc|date=2020-10-30|accessdate=2020-11-09|archive-date=2020-11-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201102150339/http://gametoc.hankyung.com/news/articleView.html?idxno=56418|dead-url=no}}</ref>。同日，[[罗技|罗技]]旗下品牌“罗技G”宣布与Riot Games合作，推出K/DA联名产品<ref>{{cite news|url=https://twitter.com/LogitechG/status/1322072029970006017|title=Calling all BLADES- it's time to style #MORE with the new League of Legends x Logitech G @KDA_MUSIC Collection, featuring the G733, G333, G305, and G840!.|website=Twitter|author=@LogitechG|date=2020-10-30|accessdate=2020-11-09|archive-date=2020-11-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201101110441/https://twitter.com/LogitechG/status/1322072029970006017|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.gizmochina.com/2020/10/30/logitech-g-launches-an-array-of-gaming-products-in-partnership-with-riot-games/|title=Logitech G launches an array of Gaming Products in partnership with Riot Games|author=Balaji S|work=Gizmochina|date=2020-10-30|accessdate=2020-11-09|archive-date=2020-11-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201105020001/https://www.gizmochina.com/2020/10/30/logitech-g-launches-an-array-of-gaming-products-in-partnership-with-riot-games/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。Riot Games还在偶像宣传活动热门地点的[[首尔地铁|首尔地铁]][[三成站|三成站]]附近、[[高速巴士客运站|高速巴士客运站]]和[[COEX商场|COEX商场]]入口处的广告看板推出户外广告，扫描广告上的[[QR码|QR码]]可参加“K/DA回归应援活动”（K/DA Comeback Support Event）<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.thisisgame.com/webzine/game/nboard/225/?n=113229|script-title=ko:라이엇, 실제 아이돌 광고처럼 지하철역에 K/DA 옥외광고 진행|trans-title=Riot, K/DA outdoor advertisement in subway station like real idol advertisement|work=This Is Game|date=2020-10-30|accessdate=2020-11-09|archive-date=2020-11-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201103004118/https://www.thisisgame.com/webzine/game/nboard/225/?n=113229|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

